(`components/settings.tsx:102-106`).

2. Request reaches `POST` handler wrapped in `withAuth`
(`app/api/user/preferences/route.ts:124-177`).

3. `withAuth` only accepts `Authorization: Bearer ...`; missing header triggers 401 early
return (`lib/auth/enhanced-middleware.ts:173-188`) before `saveUserPreferences(...)` can
run (`route.ts:162`).

4. Client code does not inspect HTTP status (only `.catch` network errors at
`components/settings.tsx:106`), so UI appears updated locally while database persistence
silently fails.
```
